'''Stun duel''' was a sport played on [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] after the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] forbade lethal duels.

It was performed with [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]] and swords set to stun so the gladiators would not be wounded lethally.

[[Gorse Bendak|Bendak Starkiller]] was a champion/survivor of old duels and declined to participate in stun duels.

